== Ikirwa k'iwawa ==[[File:Rodriguez,Rizaljf5870 06.JPG|thumb|Rodriguez,Rizaljf5870 06]]
[[Ikawa|Iwawa]] ni ikigo kimwe mubigo biri mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] ngorora muco iherereye mukirwa cya Iwawa cyo 

mukiyaga cya kivu.  mu Ntara yiburasirazuba mu karere ka [[Akarere ka Rutsiro|Rutsiro]] mu [[Umurenge wa Muhima|murenge wa Boneza]] <ref>https://www.nrs.gov.rw/index.php?id=138</ref>

iki kigo cyashinzwe ahagana  2010 ishyirirwaho abagabo barengeje imyaka 18 bakoze ibyaha

kugirango bagororwe. ndetse bahigishiriza [[Icyugaritike|imyuga]] myinshi itandukanye nimirimo yamaboko

babatoza no kureka ibiyobyabwenge nindi myitwarire idahwitse no kubasubiza mubuzima busanzwe

ndetse bagatozwa no kugira uruhare mu mibereho nubukungu niterambere ry igihugu

== Ubuzima ==
iwawa haba ibikorwa by'amadini

ubumenyi bwo mumutwe

[[Ubuvuzi mu Rwanda|ubuvuzi]] bwa burimuntu kugitike<ref>https://www.mtn.co.rw/insight/ababyeyi-bafite-abana-bagororerwa-iwawa-bagiye-koroherezwa-kubavugisha/</ref>

ubuvuzi mumatsinda

ndetse nimyitozo ngorora mubiri [sport]

== Uburezi ==
iwawa si ikigo ngorora muco gusa kuko abahabaye bahavana ubumenyi bwinshi butandukanye

harimo nko kudoda, [[Ku wa Kabiri|ubwubats]]<nowiki/>i<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/opinions/editorial-iwawa-much-more-isolated-island</ref>, ububaji, i[[Ikigo Mpuzamahanga Gishinzwe Ubucuruzi nâ€™Amajyambere Arambye|koranabuhanga]] nibindi.

== Ibyagezweho ==
hari ubuhamya bwinshi bushimishije bwabamwe mubana babaye<ref>https://www.rba.co.rw/post/Saul-to-Paul-Iwawas-drug-rehabilitation-path</ref> iwawa ndetse nababyeyi

baharereye abana babo butubwira neza imyitwarire mibi bari bafite batarajya mukigo

ngorora [[Umuco nyarwanda|muco]] ndetse nuburyo bitwaye nyuma yuko bahasoreje umwaka [[Ishuri|wishuri]] bagasubizwa

mu [[Ubuzima|buzima]] busanzwe.

== Iterambere ==
Leta yu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] yishimira cyane ko urubyiruko ruvuye iwawa ruza rwahindutse nubwo atari bose 

ariko hagaragara impinduka nziza numusaruro kuko bamwe baza bagashaka akazi abandi bakikorera

kuko abatsinze neza banahabwa bimwe mubikoresho bibafasha kwihangira imirimo

bityo bigatuma ubujura no kunywa ibiyobyabwenge bigabanuka muri [[Rwanda Rwacu|sosiyeti nyarwanda]]

